  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the investigators analysis is to identify the neural correlates of quality of life
      scores in schizophrenia. For this, the investigators will constitute group of patients
      according to their quality of life scores and the investigators will analyze their
      differences in patterns of brain structures and activations.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
